com.hannesdorfmann.mosby.retrofit

Class LceRetrofitPresenter.LceCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hannesdorfmann.mosby.retrofit.LceRetrofitPresenter.LceCallback
  • Enclosing class:
    LceRetrofitPresenter<V extends MvpLceView<M>,M>

    protected class LceRetrofitPresenter.LceCallback
extends java.lang.Object
    An out of the box Callback implementation for Retrofit requests that are associated with this presenter. It automatically calls MvpLceView.setData(Object), MvpLceView.showContent() or MvpLceView.showError(Throwable, boolean) if the view is still attached to the presenter. It also calls MvpLceView.showLoading(boolean) for you!
    Since:
    1.0.0
